Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你  叫格蕾丝来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.39,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:05.59,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,正好借此机会  把我名下的宝石都整理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.49,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,说实话我呢  有一位未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.79,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是那位非常美丽的未婚妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就是那位非常美丽的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,但她缺乏见识  还没有判断能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.29,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什么东西都捡回来收集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,明明我都提醒过她好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:33.46,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,他这话是想说  是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:38.23,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,公爵大人  其实我也有一位未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:42.56,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你说的是那位长相出众的未婚夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就是那位长相还算出众的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:50.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,对未婚妻不仅不尊重  还一点都不体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有的没的都乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,明明我都已经千叮咛万嘱咐过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:00.95,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,而且他手上动作还不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,努尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.19,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看见这些宝石了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:23.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我正是要对我非常美丽的未婚妻表示尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,才把她带来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.25,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,这样你总算能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那位长相还算出众的未婚夫的些许体贴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:38.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,温奈特公爵阁下  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.41,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:44.50,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  这就是您传说中的未婚妻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我还以为  阁下您对女性不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.90,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看来只是至今为止没找到您中意的对象而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.03,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不愧是格蕾丝夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.50,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,被看破了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我正好进了一些好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你要不要一起看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.49,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,乐意至极
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:09.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,它叫人鱼之泪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:13.86,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,曾在德瓦莎拍卖中拍出了最高价
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.34,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢  还合你心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我觉得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.53,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,当然  不管哪件都很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.23,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那么  店里全部的东西我都要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不愧是公爵阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.46,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那就请先收下这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.79,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,除了这个  其他的都送到府邸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.52,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我真的可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.94,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,跟你很配哦  莱利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不  不能太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我们也没怎么走路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.23,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我听说你给女仆放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:53.56,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:58.08,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,要是连感恩节都不能回家  也太可怜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.88,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,虽说如此  其实这只是借口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我想悠闲地独处  哪怕只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.71,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.55,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,莱利娜  我有点事要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,现在要外出一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好的  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:36.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:37.72,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:39.88,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,海莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.83,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你怎么还没走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:47.75,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,这次真的非常感谢您能给我们放假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.33,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好好享受感恩节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:52.85,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.69,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,其实  我是有点事要告诉您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.53,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:03.41,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,请绝对不要在西馆最里面的房间照镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,镜子？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.70,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像有个女仆被轮到去那值班巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,然后在那里有人和她搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:19.30,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有灵魂被封印在房间里的镜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,当与镜中灵魂的眼神对视时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.39,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像就会有人和你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.36,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,会…会说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.82,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,它会说  我什么事都会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什么事都？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.09,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,已经这个点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那我就告退了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.97,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我得去收拾回家的行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,要是真的有那样一面镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.78,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我只有一件事想问它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.32,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,故事真正的女主角  贝阿特丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:06.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,她现在身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.13,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,早知道我乖乖待在房间里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,果然好吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.08,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什么啊  原来是鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.32,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我真的得跟它对视才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:05.03,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,什么事情都会告诉我根本就不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.59,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,万一被诅咒了怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:20.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我虽然听不太清  可刚才确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.66,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.28,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎么吓成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.38,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那是因为  我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:45.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,看到了鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:50.47,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:56.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你不会觉得我在说谎吧  我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那我明天把神官叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,话说  你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.13,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我有东西忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:09.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你是不是因为担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不  我只是有东西忘拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那你等会就回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.57,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不  到明天再处理也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.72,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我送你回房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.35,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,可是  他为什么回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,虽然他说忘带东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,但会在这个时间回来拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.28,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,难道真的是因为担心我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:53.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.90,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,麻烦你特地跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.38,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那么晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.18,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,害怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.77,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,鬼魂  你看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嘛  虽说是看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:23.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不会哭丧着脸睡不着觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,够了  你快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.61,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,别那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.20,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你睡着之前我都在这陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.19,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.74,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那努尔去睡床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.39,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我睡椅子就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,干嘛…努尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.47,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.55,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,又不是第一次了  事到如今你在紧张什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:21.97,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你这种说法要是被其他人听见了会误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.91,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我可不想当让自己未婚妻睡在椅子上的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.28,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,所以麻烦睡在我身旁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,这本书  我可以看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.87,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,讲述骑士和公主之间爱而无果的恋爱小说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,可我觉得不太合你的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:47.17,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,没关系  我不在意题材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,不行  完全睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,努尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:08.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你读到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,两个主角在舞会上相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.45,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那里啊  有没有觉得令人心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:19.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,太滑稽了  反而充满了戏剧性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,滑稽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.59,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,两个人偶遇以后就一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.36,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,因为一场偶然的事故又不得不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,几个月后  又再次碰巧在舞会上相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,一系列都是巧合所以滑稽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.48,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,未免也太不现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,明明自己也是恋爱小说的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.33,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,一昧追求现实性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你永远体会不到心动和浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你读到骑士告白的地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.15,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你快看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,超级心动的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.29,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,莱利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:14:59.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你不睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.83,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.50,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊…是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:11.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我变得有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.21,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,奥布莱恩伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.90,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊  温奈特公爵阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.71,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.95,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,听说你为执行任务而远征中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.64,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是的  已经圆满完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  陛下在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,等等  阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.15,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,可以请您稍微等一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,西亚特里斯陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:07.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我是娜奥美·奥布莱恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:12.34,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.33,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,您该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:24.18,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,娜奥美  你为何如此神经大条
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.98,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你至少应该要敲门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我敲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:36.36,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,至今为止您一次也没听到我的敲门声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.81,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:41.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,或许您应该去检查一下您的听力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:45.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊…说起来感觉好像听到了敲门声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.94,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊不  确实听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那就最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.78,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,哦…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.11,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我从刚刚那位女士那里听到了有趣的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:57.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.99,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,听说我在生死之间徘徊的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我那可爱的弟弟努尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.03,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有了一位深爱着的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像是叫…莱莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.48,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,生死之间徘徊也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.43,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,而且不是叫莱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.75,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是麦米伦家族的莱利娜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.46,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,查尔莫斯王国的现任国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:29.60,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,在床上还能听到这样的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.62,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,这足以说明我有多爱我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,陛下  你看起来已经痊愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.51,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,奇斯  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,努尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.07,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:47.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,哦~努尔  你在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.26,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像有个人不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,那个红色眼睛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,亚丹的话有别的事情还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:59.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,嗯…还真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.93,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,既然大家都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.80,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我们为了明天举杯庆祝一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,会期终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:19.09,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,被否决的法案在几年内不能再被提出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.91,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,所以我们暂时阻止了「暴发户防止法」的成立
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.85,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,也就是说没必要再把玉玺藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.94,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,关于陛下的落马事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.35,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,从马的体内检测到了兴奋剂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:39.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,果然…从那匹马奇怪的样子来看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.78,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,就知道不可能是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.32,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,这是由贝内特伯爵精心策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.63,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,暗杀国王计划的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.53,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,贝内特啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:54.47,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我要是死了那家伙肯定是最开心的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:20:00.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,贝内特伯爵的话会将陛下的尸体挂在广场上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.14,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,再在旁边跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,肯定还会唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:08.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你总是能把这么吓人的事情说得这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.24,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,您误会了  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.05,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  努尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.02,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,听说你多了个未婚妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,名字好像是叫…拉莉安娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.56,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,刚刚已经告诉过您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.98,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是莱利娜·麦米伦大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,对对  莱利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.58,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,在我因服用镇静剂而昏迷的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,你的心境发生了什么变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.97,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:39.35,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.25,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我给您放在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.67,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  海莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,秋雨时期已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.31,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,很快要真正开始变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,秋雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.12,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好像想起了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.10,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:21.40,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,「会期终于结束，玉玺的行踪何去何从？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:23.84,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.27,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,我为什么会忘掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.79,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,会期结束的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.77,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,在温奈特家族的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:47.65,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,按照原著的话  她会出现在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.92,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,金发的  贝阿特丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:11.06,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  你的婚约可以作废了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.59,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}変わりのない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.64,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}夢の続きを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:20.40,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}誰かの私でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:25.86,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(600,800)\blur5}それでも今日も息をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:32.20,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}星降る夜に流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:39.12,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}あなたは何処へ向かうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:46.72,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}物語にはない　終わらない運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:52.01,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.73,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}Always and Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:08.32,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}ただ　生きるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:16.83,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}揺れた灯りが儚く消える前に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:22.79,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}遠く　遠く　離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:31.68,Kanojo ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}強く　強く　愛せますように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.59,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}未曾改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.64,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}梦境的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:20.40,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}无论是谁  亦或是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:25.86,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(600,800)\blur5}即便如此今天也依然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:32.20,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}在那个星河流淌的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:39.12,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}你将前往何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:46.72,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}故事中不存在的  未完的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:52.01,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}若能够实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.73,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}Always and Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:08.32,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}只是  活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:16.83,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}在摇曳的灯光飘渺着熄灭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:22.79,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}即使离得很远  很远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:31.68,Kanojo ed cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,800)\blur5}也希望能够坚强地爱下去
